* Apocope
* Clipping (morphology)
* Clipping (phonetics)
* Deletion (phonology)
* Elision
* Epenthesis, the &quot;addition&quot; of sounds to the interior of a word
* Poetic contraction
* Synaeresis
* Synalepha
* Syncopation in music
* Vowel reduction

