<text>The term State Normal and Industrial School may refer to:

* A former name of Alabama A&amp;M University
* A former name of the University of North Carolina at Greensboro
* The North Dakota State Normal and Industrial School, a former college in Ellendale, North Dakota
* The St. Petersburg Normal and Industrial School, a former college in St. Petersburg, Florida, merged into the University of Florida in 1905</text><links>
